== Start Terminal Emulator in a Disposable ==

Terminal emulator <code>qterminal</code> can be started via the GUI or on the command line.

{{Box|text=
<u>If you are using a GUI</u>, complete the following steps.

<code>Qubes App Launcher (blue/grey "Q")</code> &rarr; <code>Disposable: {{whonix-ws-dvm}}</code> &rarr; <code>QTerminal</code>

<u>If you are using a terminal</u>, complete the following steps.

{{CodeSelect|code=
qvm-run --dispvm={{whonix-ws-dvm}} qterminal
}}
}}

